            "id": "20260218A06T7900",
            "title": "深夜美股全线大涨！芯片股走强，美光科技涨5%，黄金重回5000美元",
            "image": "https://inews.gtimg.com/om_ls/OYSPtyZnbU-xUaNGWxY7BQ9veUkhixOGAteInlzmXmu4kAA_870492/0",
            "link": "https://new.qq.com/rain/a/20260218A06T7900",
            "author": "名扬四海",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-18 23:32:56",
            "description": "<div class=\"rich_media_content\"><section data-exeditor-arbitrary-box=\"wrap\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(62, 62, 62);font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:justify\"><section data-exeditor-arbitrary-box=\"wrap\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(25, 67, 115);font-size:15px;letter-spacing:2px;padding:0px 10px;text-align:right\"><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:left\"><span style=\"color:rgb(25, 67, 115)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:2px\">记者丨金珊</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:left\"><span style=\"color:rgb(25, 67, 115)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:2px\">编辑丨江佩霞</span></span></span></p></section><section data-exeditor-arbitrary-box=\"wrap\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(56, 54, 53);letter-spacing:1px;line-height:2;padding:0px 12px\"><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\"><br/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\">2月18日晚，美股开盘集体上涨，截至23:25，道指涨0.58%，纳指涨1.16%，标普500指数涨0.77%。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\"><br/></span></span></span></p><section data-exeditor-arbitrary-box=\"image-box\" style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/OWP3YTKdfUL_YTFziW5hzT_M9mC917-l-RlC1DovD5qiQAA/641\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/OWP3YTKdfUL_YTFziW5hzT_M9mC917-l-RlC1DovD5qiQAA/641\" style=\"border-radius:6px;display:inline-block;max-width:100%;width:100%;height:100%\"/></section><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\"><br/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\">大型科技股涨多跌少，<span dt-eid=\"\" dt-params=\"\"><span class=\"qnt-link\"><span>英伟达</span></span></span>涨超2%，消息面上，据财联社报道，Meta加码英伟达，未来数年部署数百万颗芯片，首次采用Grace CPU。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\"><br/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\">芯片股普涨，费城半导体指数涨1.72%，<span dt-eid=\"\" dt-params=\"\"><span class=\"qnt-link\"><span>美光科技</span></span></span>涨超5%，<span dt-eid=\"\" dt-params=\"\"><span class=\"qnt-link\"><span>阿斯麦</span></span></span>、<span dt-eid=\"\" dt-params=\"\"><span class=\"qnt-link\"><span>应用材料</span></span></span>等涨超2%，存储芯片巨头<span dt-eid=\"\" dt-params=\"\"><span class=\"qnt-link\"><span>西部数据</span></span></span>大涨4%，消息面上，据券商中国报道，西部数据宣布将出售其所持有的闪迪全部普通股，交易规模约30.9亿美元（约合人民币213亿元）。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\"><br/></span></span></span></p><section data-exeditor-arbitrary-box=\"image-box\" style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/O1NCHcNaLBVXq4zwxDbCp3GAkuPVgQGOG81_rAgEphADMAA/641\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/O1NCHcNaLBVXq4zwxDbCp3GAkuPVgQGOG81_rAgEphADMAA/641\" style=\"border-radius:6px;display:inline-block;max-width:100%;width:100%;height:100%\"/></section><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\"><br/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\">黄金概念股大涨，<span dt-eid=\"\" dt-params=\"\"><span class=\"qnt-link\"><span>科尔黛伦矿业</span></span></span>涨3.5%，<span dt-eid=\"\" dt-params=\"\"><span class=\"qnt-link\"><span>Vista黄金</span></span></span>涨2.8%，First Majestic Silver、Endeavour Silver涨2.6%，<span dt-eid=\"\" dt-params=\"\"><span class=\"qnt-link\"><span>埃氏金业</span></span></span>涨2.4%，<span dt-eid=\"\" dt-params=\"\"><span class=\"qnt-link\"><span>纽曼矿业</span></span></span>、泛美白银涨超2%，金田、哈莫尼黄金涨1.2%。消息面上，</span></span></span><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\">晚间黄金白银双双急速拉升</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\">，现货黄金涨超2.6%，重新站上5000美元，现货白银涨幅扩大至6%，报78美元/盎司。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\"><br/></span></span></span></p><section data-exeditor-arbitrary-box=\"image-box\" style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/ONZuqIWWX-Saqq3csI7nApknTrkKs0ufFQBXGFdigO4Z4AA/641\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/ONZuqIWWX-Saqq3csI7nApknTrkKs0ufFQBXGFdigO4Z4AA/641\" style=\"border-radius:6px;display:inline-block;max-width:100%;width:540px;height:100%\"/></section><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\"><br/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\">中概股方面，纳斯达克中国金龙指数涨0.49%，阿特斯太阳能涨近3%，百度集团、<span dt-eid=\"\" dt-params=\"\"><span class=\"qnt-link\"><span>阿里巴巴</span></span></span>涨超1%，文远知行跌超2%，爱奇艺跌超1%。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\"><br/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\">据上海证券报，2月18日，高瓴旗下专注二级市场投资的基金管理平台HHLR Advisors公布了截至2025年四季度末的美股持仓情况。数据显示，截至2025年末，HHLR共持有33只美股上市公司，</span></span></span><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\">中概股仍是其核心配置资产</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\">。从调仓动作来看，HHLR去年显著增持了阿里巴巴和拼多多，减持网易、富途控股等标的，持仓进一步集中在电商龙头、生物医药和科技方向。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\"><br/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\">此外，</span></span></span><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\">国际油价涨势强劲，美油、布油期货涨幅扩大至3%</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\">，分别报64.13美元/桶和69.441美元/桶。消息面上，据央视新闻报道，</span></span></span><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\">斯洛伐克政府因乌克兰中断俄罗斯石油过境运输，宣布自19日起进入国家石油紧急状态</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\">。斯洛伐克政府批准从国家紧急储备中借给斯洛伐克炼油厂最多25万吨石油，约够一个月用量，以确保市场供应稳定。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\"><br/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\">加密货币主要币种由跌转涨，比特币重回67000美元上方，过去24小时，全市场超8万人爆仓。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\"><br/></span></span></span></p></section><section data-exeditor-arbitrary-box=\"wrap\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;line-height:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-top:10px;text-align:center\"><section data-exeditor-arbitrary-box=\"image-box\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;display:inline-block;height:auto;line-height:0;max-width:100%;vertical-align:middle;width:95%\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/OGVskDlAaCrk43CayJFTQJBIe_VHLswirQ2ASS9_tLVQUAA/641\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/OGVskDlAaCrk43CayJFTQJBIe_VHLswirQ2ASS9_tLVQUAA/641\" style=\"border-radius:6px;display:inline-block;max-width:100%;width:100%;height:100%\"/></section></section><section data-exeditor-arbitrary-box=\"wrap\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(56, 54, 53);letter-spacing:1px;line-height:2;padding:0px 12px\"><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\"><br/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\">据央视财经报道，市场静待即将公布的美联储1月货币政策会议纪要以及美国重要通胀数据，研判美联储货币政策走向。</span></span></span><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\">目前芝商所美联储观察工具显示，市场预期美联储大概率将在6月开启降息。</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\">此外，金银价格在大幅下跌后迎来技术性反弹，叠加美伊谈判、俄乌和谈仍存变数，避险需求也在一定程度上对贵金属价格形成支撑。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\"><br/></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\">央视新闻最新报道，据俄罗斯方面18日消息，</span></span></span><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\">俄罗斯、美国和乌克兰在为期两天的日内瓦三方会谈期间未签署任何文件。由于各方立场相左，有关政治问题的会谈在17日陷入停滞</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\">。另据新华社报道，乌克兰总统泽连斯基18日表示，在为期两天的日内瓦三方会谈中，乌克兰、美国和俄罗斯在军事层面表现出建设性态度，但在政治层面仍存在分歧。泽连斯基表示，政治层面议题涉及领土及扎波罗热核电站等敏感问题。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\"><br/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(160, 160, 160)\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\">（声明：文章内容仅供参考，不构成投资建议。投资者据此操作，风险自担。） </span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(56, 54, 53)\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\"><br/></span></span></span></p></section><section data-exeditor-arbitrary-box=\"wrap\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(160, 160, 160);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;padding:0px 10px\"><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:center\"><span style=\"color:rgb(160, 160, 160)\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\">出品丨21财经客户端 21世纪经济报道</span></span></span></p></section></section></div>",
